<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="platform-n">platform <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'plætfɔːm/    美 /'plætfɔːrm/  </p>
<p>[C] </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>平台；讲台；戏台；站台：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I dream of standing on the platform in the classroom and giving lessons to lovely boys and girls. 
我梦想站在教室的讲台上，给可爱的男孩女孩们上课。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The train for Cambridge will depart from platform 9.
开往剑桥的火车将从9号站台开出。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>social media platforms such as Wechat and Facebook
微信和Facebook等社交平台</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>e-commerce platforms
电子商务平台</p></div></div>